data.description: The Belfort floorplan features a first-floor owner's suite with an oversized great room and large kitchen island. Three additional bedrooms with walk-in closets and a loft area, perfect for an additional entertainment space, can be found on the second level. Owners will enjoy world class amenities including resort style pool, club house, indoor pickle ball court, bocce ball court, playground, gas fire pit, and boat launch. Photos are a depiction of a similar home.
